msg: Removed parameter from the catalina-container setup that is deprecated:
Deprecated. Unused, removed in Tomcat 8. See org.apache.catalina.connector.Connector.setEnableLookups(boolean).
and according to the above notes I have enabled the same behavior using the enableLookups flag in the Connectors.
This change resolves a warning during compilation but requires more testing.
